                <div class="terms-content">
                    <p>
                        Welcome to <strong>ArtOnline.</strong> By accessing this website, creating an account, or submitting a commission request, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions.
                    </p>

                    <h3>1. Use of the Service</h3>
                    <p>
                        This platform is intended for submitting and managing digital art commission requests between clients and the artist. Users agree to use the service only for lawful and appropriate purposes.
                    </p>

                    <h3>2. Accounts</h3>
                    <p>
                        Clients are required to create an account to access certain features such as submitting and tracking commissions. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials.
                    </p>

                    <h3>3. Commission Requests</h3>
                    <p>
                        Submitting a commission request does not guarantee acceptance. All requests are subject to review and approval by the artist.
                    </p>

                    <h3>4. Commission Process</h3>
                    <p>
                        Once a commission is accepted, both client and artist may communicate and agree on pricing, style, deadlines, and revisions. Work will only begin after mutual agreement.
                    </p>

                    <h3>5. Payment Terms</h3>
                    <p>
                        Payment arrangements are handled directly between the client and the artist unless otherwise stated. The platform does not automatically process payments.
                    </p>

                    <h3>6. Revisions and Changes</h3>
                    <p>
                        The number of revisions allowed depends on the agreement between the client and artist before or during the commission process.
                    </p>

                    <h3>7. Cancellations</h3>
                    <p>
                        The artist reserves the right to accept or decline any request. Clients may cancel pending requests before acceptance through communications. Accepted commissions may only be canceled under agreed conditions.
                    </p>

                    <h3>8. Content Restrictions</h3>
                    <p>
                        The artist will not accept commissions involving NSFW content, explicit violence, hate speech, illegal material, or any content deemed inappropriate or unethical.
                    </p>

                    <h3>9. Intellectual Property</h3>
                    <p>
                        Unless otherwise agreed, the artist retains the rights to display completed works in their portfolio or gallery for promotional purposes.
                    </p>

                    <h3>10. Limitation of Liability</h3>
                    <p>
                        The platform and artist are not responsible for any indirect losses, delays, or misunderstandings arising from commission transactions.
                    </p>

                    <h3>11. Changes to Terms</h3>
                    <p>
                        These Terms and Conditions may be updated at any time. Continued use of the website constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
                    </p>

                    <h3>12. Contact</h3>
                    <p>
                        For concerns or inquiries regarding these Terms and Conditions, users may contact the artist through the provided communication channels.
                    </p>

                    <p class="terms-ack">By using this website, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to these Terms and Conditions.</p>
                    <p class="terms-date">Last Updated: June 06, 2026</p>
